2002-06-02  Fred Kiefer <FredKiefer@gmx.de>

	* Source/win32/WIN32Server.m
	Treat NSBackingStoreRetained the same as NSBackingStoreBuffered, 
	just as the X backends do. 
	* Source/winlib/WIN32GState.m
